:{{DIcon|Talk}} How old are you?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502120103-->
::'''Yanming:''' Uh, I'll tell you I'm old enough. The specific age isn't important.
::'''Yanming:''' Whether it's in the hundreds or thousands, it will still sound ancient to you.
::'''Yanming:''' Let me give you some advice: Never ask a girl on Xianzhou that question... Or in any world, for that matter.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} What do you do here?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502120107-->
::'''Yanming:''' Simply put, I'm in charge of relaying orders from the Sky-Faring Commission to the guilds, and passing guild requests back.
::'''Yanming:''' The Celestial Guild is not one big body but a consortium of many smaller guilds, so I help both sides communicate with each other.
::'''Yanming:''' However, several centuries back, I was a captain of a trade ship. Centuries before that, I was a business professor in a lyceum... Never mind, they're just jobs.
::'''Yanming:''' The more experienced you are, the more you'll realize that how serious you treat a job is how serious it treats you.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} About the guild...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502120112-->
::'''Yanming:''' Ever since the calamities ended and the Luofu settled down, guilds have been Xianzhou's lifeblood. Some of them are government-backed, and some are purely civilian.
::'''Yanming:''' Tingyun is the Head Representative of the intergalactic merchant guild, Whistling Flames. She's witty and a great communicator. She was born to do business.
::'''Yanming:''' Have you heard of the Grand Fair in Xianzhou? Tingyun turned that into an intergalactic festival.
::'''Yanming:''' "Sea of fiery lights illuminate the countless suburbs, while feasts and songs unveil nights of innumerable glows"... Nicely done.
::'''Yanming:''' Pardon me for getting off-tangent, but you probably realize how vital the guilds are now...
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} About Madam Yukong...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502120118-->
::'''Yanming:''' You could say Madam Yukong is my boss. Her competence is undeniable, but her flexible adaptability to different situations is even more impressive.
::'''Yanming:''' Although she claimed to be lacking in trade acumen, I beg to differ, as she could often shut schemers and opportunists down without a word, and few can manage to play with words before her.
::'''Yanming:''' To me, the end is the same even when the approach is not. The negotiations go a lot smoother with Madam Yukong present.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} That's all. I'll take my leave now.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502120122-->
::'''Yanming:''' Sure, have a nice day.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
