:::'''Yanming:''' Madam Yukong entrusted me with the Whistling Flames to take care of for Tingyun. Looking at her former subordinates, I honestly didn't know how to explain the situation to them...
:::'''Yanming:''' *sigh* ...The world is full of jokes I can't bring myself to laugh at.
:;(If {{Mission|A New Venture on the Eighth Dawn (Trailblaze Mission)|showChapter=0}} has not been completed)
:::'''Yanming:''' Many of my colleagues believe she is still alive and pledge to find her. As for me... I'm more realistic.
:::'''Yanming:''' Having said that, I'm still looking for her alongside everyone else, simply because Madam Yukong thinks she is alive and wants to find her. I'll follow Madam Yukong to find her - it's as simple as that.
:::'''Yanming:''' Even though I don't believe it, I won't have Madam Yukong getting too deeply involved in the matter alone.
